<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Informe Semanal - DXA Retorno Total</title>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <style>
            :root {
                --navy: #004F3A;
                --turquoise: #007A5E;
                --turquoise-light: rgba(0,122,94,0.07);
                --turquoise-mid: rgba(0,122,94,0.15);
                --turquoise-glow: rgba(0,122,94,0.22);
                --gray-dark: #3A3F45;
                --gray-mid: #6E7480;
                --gray-light: #E4E8E6;
                --white: #FFFFFF;
                --red-soft: #C94040;
                --green-soft: #007A5E;
            }

            * {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }

            html {
                scroll-behavior: smooth;
            }

            body {
                font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif;
                color: var(--gray-dark);
                font-size: 15px;
                line-height: 1.7;
                -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
                background: var(--white);
                overflow-x: hidden;
            }

            nav {
                position: fixed;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                z-index: 100;
                padding: 0 48px;
                height: 88px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 40px;
                background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97);
                backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
                border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
                transition: border-color .3s;
            }

            nav.scrolled {
                border-bottom-color: rgba(0,122,94,0.2);
            }

            .nav-brand {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                text-decoration: none;
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .nav-brand-text {
                font-size: 13px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--navy);
                letter-spacing: .3px;
                line-height: 1.2;
            }

            .nav-brand-sub {
                font-size: 10px;
                font-weight: 500;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                display: block;
                letter-spacing: .5px;
            }

            .nav-links {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 32px;
                list-style: none;
            }

            .nav-links a {
                font-size: 11px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                text-decoration: none;
                letter-spacing: .5px;
                transition: color .2s;
            }

            .nav-links a:hover {
                color: var(--navy);
            }

            .hero {
                min-height: 72vh;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                position: relative;
                padding: 88px 48px 0;
                overflow: hidden;
            }

            .hero-grid-bg {
                position: absolute;
                inset: 0;
                background-image: linear-gradient(var(--gray-light) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gray-light) 1px,transparent 1px);
                background-size: 80px 80px;
                opacity: .35;
                mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 55% at 50% 45%,black 20%,transparent 70%);
                -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 55% at 50% 45%,black 20%,transparent 70%);
            }

            .hero-line {
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                right: 22%;
                width: 1px;
                height: 100%;
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,var(--turquoise-mid) 30%,var(--turquoise-mid) 70%,transparent);
            }

            .hero-orb {
                position: absolute;
                width: 450px;
                height: 450px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background: radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,122,94,0.13) 0%,transparent 70%);
                top: 50%;
                left: 50%;
                transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
                pointer-events: none;
            }

            .hero-content {
                position: relative;
                z-index: 2;
                max-width: 700px;
                padding: 72px 0 64px;
                animation: fadeUp .9s ease-out;
                text-align: center;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }

            .hero-eyebrow {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 10px;
                font-size: 11px;
                font-weight: 600;
                letter-spacing: 2.5px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }

            .hero-eyebrow::before {
                content: '';
                width: 24px;
                height: 1px;
                background: var(--turquoise);
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 48px;
                font-weight: 800;
                color: var(--navy);
                line-height: 1.1;
                letter-spacing: -1.5px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .hero h1 .accent {
                position: relative;
                display: inline-block;
            }

            .hero h1 .accent::after {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                bottom: 3px;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                height: 8px;
                background: var(--turquoise-glow);
                border-radius: 4px;
                z-index: -1;
            }

            .hero-desc {
                font-size: 16px;
                font-weight: 400;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                line-height: 1.8;
                max-width: 560px;
                margin: 0 auto 40px;
            }

            .hero-chips {
                display: flex;
                gap: 12px;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .chip {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 8px;
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--navy);
                background: var(--white);
                border: 1px solid rgba(0,122,94,0.25);
                padding: 10px 18px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }

            .chip .dot {
                width: 6px;
                height: 6px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                background: var(--turquoise);
            }

            .context-section {
                padding: 0 48px;
                max-width: 960px;
                margin: -16px auto 0;
                position: relative;
                z-index: 2;
            }

            .context-box {
                background: var(--white);
                border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
                border-top: 3px solid var(--turquoise);
                border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
                padding: 32px 36px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .context-box h3 {
                font-size: 12px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--navy);
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 1.2px;
                margin-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .context-box p {
                font-size: 14px;
                color: var(--gray-dark);
                line-height: 1.8;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }

            .context-box p:last-child {
                margin-bottom: 0;
            }

            .context-box strong {
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--navy);
            }

            .note-box {
                max-width: 960px;
                margin: 32px auto 0;
                padding: 0 48px;
            }

            .note-inner {
                background: var(--turquoise-light);
                border: 1px solid var(--turquoise-mid);
                border-radius: 10px;
                padding: 24px 28px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .note-label {
                font-size: 9px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                letter-spacing: 2px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

            .note-text {
                font-size: 13.5px;
                color: var(--navy);
                font-weight: 500;
                line-height: 1.7;
            }

            .kpis {
                padding: 48px 48px 0;
                max-width: 960px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 16px;
                background: transparent;
                border: none;
            }

            .kpi-grid {
                display: grid;
                gap: 1px;
                background: var(--gray-light);
                border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
                border-radius: 12px;
                overflow: hidden;
            }

            .kpi-grid-mid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
            }

            .kpi-grid-bot {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
            }

            .kpi-aum {
                background: var(--white);
                border-left: 3px solid var(--turquoise) !important;
            }

            .kpi-aum-value {
                font-size: 22px;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                font-weight: 800;
            }

            .kpi-card {
                background: var(--white);
                padding: 22px 24px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .kpi-label {
                font-size: 9px;
                font-weight: 600;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 1.2px;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .kpi-value {
                font-size: 20px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--navy);
                line-height: 1;
            }

            .kpi-value.negative {
                color: var(--red-soft);
            }

            .kpi-detail {
                font-size: 10px;
                font-weight: 500;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                margin-top: 6px;
            }

            .kpi-compare {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .kpi-col {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 5px;
            }

            .kpi-col-label {
                font-size: 8px;
                font-weight: 700;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                padding: 2px 8px;
                border-radius: 4px;
                background: var(--gray-light);
            }

            .kpi-col-label.fund {
                background: var(--turquoise-light);
                color: var(--turquoise);
            }

            .kpi-col-value {
                font-size: 18px;
                font-weight: 700;
                line-height: 1;
            }

            .kpi-col-value.positive {
                color: var(--green-soft);
            }

            .kpi-col-value.neg {
                color: var(--red-soft);
            }

            .kpi-divider-v {
                width: 1px;
                background: var(--gray-light);
            }

            .market-report {
                max-width: 960px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 80px 48px 0;
            }

            .report-header {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
                gap: 6px;
            }

            .report-brand {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 4px;
            }

            .report-brand-name {
                font-size: 18px;
                font-weight: 800;
                color: var(--navy);
                letter-spacing: -.5px;
            }

            .report-brand-sub {
                font-size: 10px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                letter-spacing: 1.5px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .report-meta {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .report-meta-label {
                font-size: 9px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                letter-spacing: 2.5px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

            .report-meta-detail {
                font-size: 10px;
                font-weight: 400;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                margin-top: 2px;
            }

            .report-divider {
                height: 1px;
                background: var(--gray-light);
                margin-bottom: 28px;
                position: relative;
            }

            .report-divider-accent {
                height: 3px;
                width: 80px;
                background: var(--turquoise);
                margin: -1px auto 0;
                border-radius: 2px;
            }

            .report-title {
                font-size: 26px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--navy);
                text-align: center;
                line-height: 1.2;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

            .report-subtitle {
                font-size: 14px;
                font-weight: 500;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                text-align: center;
                margin-bottom: 32px;
            }

            .insight-box {
                background: var(--navy);
                border-radius: 8px;
                padding: 24px 28px;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
                text-align: center;
                border-left: 4px solid var(--turquoise);
            }

            .insight-label {
                font-size: 10px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #5DFFC7;
                letter-spacing: 2.5px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                margin-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .insight-box p {
                font-size: 15.5px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: #FFFFFF;
                line-height: 1.85;
                letter-spacing: .1px;
            }

            .insight-box p strong {
                color: #5DFFC7;
                font-weight: 700;
            }

            .report-section {
                margin-bottom: 32px;
            }

            .report-section-header {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 12px;
                margin-bottom: 14px;
            }

            .report-num {
                font-size: 10px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                background: var(--turquoise-light);
                width: 32px;
                height: 32px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                flex-shrink: 0;
                border: 1px solid var(--turquoise-mid);
            }

            .report-num-alt {
                background: rgba(0,79,58,0.08);
                color: var(--navy);
                border: 1px solid rgba(0,79,58,0.15);
            }

            .report-section-title {
                font-size: 14px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--navy);
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: .8px;
            }

            .report-section-line {
                height: 1px;
                background: var(--gray-light);
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }

            .report-body {
                font-size: 13.5px;
                font-weight: 400;
                color: var(--gray-dark);
                line-height: 1.8;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .report-body strong {
                color: var(--navy);
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            .report-next-week {
                background: rgba(0,122,94,0.04);
                border: 1px solid rgba(0,122,94,0.15);
                border-radius: 8px;
                padding: 24px 28px;
            }

            .report-footer {
                margin-top: 40px;
                padding-top: 20px;
                border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
                font-size: 10px;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                opacity: .6;
                text-align: center;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .footer {
                max-width: 960px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 56px 48px 48px;
            }

            .footer-inner {
                border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
                padding-top: 32px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 12px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .footer-brand {
                font-size: 13px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--navy);
            }

            .footer-brand-sub {
                font-size: 10px;
                color: var(--turquoise);
                font-weight: 600;
                letter-spacing: .5px;
            }

            .footer-left {
                font-size: 11px;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                line-height: 1.8;
            }

            .footer-right {
                font-size: 10px;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                opacity: .5;
                max-width: 500px;
                text-align: center;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .chart-section {
                max-width: 960px;
                margin: 48px auto 0;
                padding: 0 48px;
            }

            .chart-box {
                background: var(--white);
                border: 1px solid rgba(0,122,94,0.2);
                border-top: 3px solid var(--turquoise);
                border-radius: 12px;
                padding: 32px 36px;
            }

            .chart-header {
                text-align: center;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }

            .chart-title {
                font-size: 15px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: var(--navy);
                letter-spacing: -.3px;
            }

            .chart-subtitle {
                font-size: 11px;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                margin-top: 4px;
            }

            .chart-legend {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 20px;
                margin-top: 14px;
            }

            .legend-dot {
                width: 10px;
                height: 10px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                display: inline-block;
                margin-right: 5px;
                vertical-align: middle;
            }

            .legend-dot.fund {
                background: #007A5E;
            }

            .legend-dot.merval {
                background: #1A4FA0;
            }

            .legend-label {
                font-size: 11px;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--gray-dark);
                vertical-align: middle;
            }

            .chart-area {
                position: relative;
                height: 320px;
            }

            @media(max-width: 768px) {
                .chart-section {
                    padding:0 20px;
                }

                .chart-area {
                    height: 220px;
                }
            }

            .nav-logo-dracma {
                height: 52px;
                width: auto;
            }

            .nav-logo-siglo {
                height: 66px;
                width: auto;
            }

            .nav-brand-sep {
                font-size: 20px;
                font-weight: 300;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                margin: 0 10px;
            }

            .report-logos {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 20px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .report-logo-dracma {
                height: 52px;
                width: auto;
            }

            .report-logo-siglo {
                height: 66px;
                width: auto;
            }

            .report-logo-sep {
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 300;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
            }

            .footer-logos {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 16px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .footer-logo-dracma {
                height: 32px;
                width: auto;
                opacity: .7;
            }

            .footer-logo-siglo {
                height: 42px;
                width: auto;
                opacity: .7;
            }

            .footer-logo-sep {
                font-size: 16px;
                font-weight: 300;
                color: var(--gray-mid);
                opacity: .7;
            }

            @keyframes fadeUp {
                from {
                    opacity: 0;
                    transform: translateY(20px);
                }

                to {
                    opacity: 1;
                    transform: translateY(0);
                }
            }

            .reveal {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(16px);
                transition: opacity .65s ease,transform .65s ease;
            }

            .reveal.visible {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            @media(max-width: 768px) {
                nav {
                    padding:0 20px;
                }

                .nav-links {
                    display: none;
                }

                .hero {
                    padding: 64px 20px 0;
                    min-height: auto;
                }

                .hero h1 {
                    font-size: 32px;
                }

                .hero-chips {
                    flex-direction: column;
                }

                .context-section,.note-box,.kpis,.market-report,.footer {
                    padding-left: 20px;
                    padding-right: 20px;
                }

                .kpi-grid-mid,.kpi-grid-bot {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                }

                .report-header {
                    flex-direction: column;
                    gap: 12px;
                    align-items: center;
                }

                .report-meta {
                    align-items: center;
                    text-align: center;
                }
            }

            @media print {
                nav {
                    display: none;
                }

                .hero {
                    min-height: auto;
                    padding-top: 24px;
                }

                .hero h1 {
                    font-size: 28px;
                }

                body {
                    font-size: 12px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav id="navbar">
            <a href="#" class="nav-brand">
                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Dracma Asset Management" class="nav-logo-dracma">
                <span class="nav-brand-sep">×</span>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Universidad Siglo 21" class="nav-logo-siglo">
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li>
                    <a href="#contexto">Contexto</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#mercados">Mercados</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-grid-bg"></div>
            <div class="hero-line"></div>
            <div class="hero-orb"></div>
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-eyebrow">DXA Retorno Total &middot;Informe Semanal</div>
                <h1>
                    Reporte Semanal de <span class="accent">Operaciones</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-desc">Resumen de la actividad del portafolio durante la semana, con foco en las operaciones m &aacute;s relevantes y el posicionamiento estrat &eacute;gico en renta variable argentina.</p>
                <div class="hero-chips">
                    <div class="chip">
                        <span class="dot"></span>
                        Fondo Dedicado: Fundaci &oacute;n Siglo 21
                    </div>
                    <div class="chip">
                        <span class="dot"></span>
                        Estrategia: 100% Renta Variable Argentina
                    </div>
                    <div class="chip">
                        <span class="dot"></span>
                        16 &mdash;19 de Junio, 2026
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <div class="context-section reveal" id="contexto">
            <div class="context-box">
                <h3>Contexto de la semana</h3>
                <p>
                    La cartera del <strong>Fondo DXA Retorno Total</strong>
                    , dedicado exclusivamente a la <strong>Fundaci &oacute;n Universidad Empresarial Siglo 21</strong>
                    , mantuvo su posicionamiento en renta variable argentina durante la semana. El portafolio se benefici &oacute;del <strong>fuerte impulso del sector bancario</strong>
                    (BBAR +9%), que compensó la corrección en el segmento petrolero a raíz del acuerdo entre EEUU e Irán y la consiguiente caída del Brent.
                </p>
                <p>
                    La baja del <strong>riesgo país por debajo de los 425 puntos</strong>
                    —mínimo histórico reciente— junto con el upgrade de S &amp;P, mejoró significativamente el contexto para las acciones argentinas, aunque el inicio del ciclo restrictivo de la Fed bajo Kevin Warsh y la fortaleza del dólar (DXY +3%) pusieron un límite a la suba en la segunda mitad de la semana.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="note-box reveal">
            <div class="note-inner">
                <div class="note-label">Pol &iacute;tica de inversi &oacute;n</div>
